== 封鎖 ==
=== 中国大陆 ===
纽约时报的网站在未知时间被[[中国大陆|中国大陆]][[防火长城|防火长城]]屏蔽，[[湯馬斯·佛里曼|湯馬斯·佛里曼]]在2001年8月和[[江泽民|江泽民]]见面并询问此事，江泽民表示不知情，时报网站几天后被解除屏蔽<ref name=craig>{{Cite web|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20170401/the-new-york-times-vs-the-great-firewall-of-china/|title=纽约时报中文网的“前世今生”|author=CRAIG S. SMITH|date=2017-04-01|access-date=2021-07-30|archive-date=2021-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609160134/https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20170401/the-new-york-times-vs-the-great-firewall-of-china/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
網站于2008年10月16日（周四）晚又被防火长城屏蔽<ref>{{cite web|title=China Blocks Access to The Times’s Web Site|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/20/world/asia/20china.html|date=2008-10-19|accessdate=2012-10-31|language=en|publisher=纽约时报|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501082733/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/20/world/asia/20china.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，本次封锁于20日被解除<ref>{{cite web|title=China Unblocks The Times’s Web Site|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/23/world/asia/23china.html|date=2008-10-22|accessdate=2012-10-31|language=en|publisher=纽约时报|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501082738/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/23/world/asia/23china.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

